nav_platform:"Platform",nav_modules:"Modules",nav_proces:"How it works",nav_projecten:"Projects",nav_usps:"Why us",nav_infra:"Infrastructure",nav_contact:"Contact",
hero_h1:'25 AI Agents. One Platform.<br><span>Zero compromises.</span>',
hero_p:"The complete AI platform for tourism destinations. From website to chatbot, from content to commerce \u2014 fully automated, multilingual, and local.",
hero_cta1:"Request Demo",hero_cta2:"Discover Platform \u2193",
badge_eu:"EU-First",badge_eu_d:"All data, AI and infrastructure within the EU",
badge_wl:"White Label",badge_wl_d:"Your brand, domain and colour palette",
badge_l2l:"Local2Local",badge_l2l_d:"Local knowledge from locals for locals",
badge_mt:"Multi-Tenancy",badge_mt_d:"One platform, unlimited destinations",
plat_label:"The Platform",plat_title:"AI-driven. Human controlled.",
plat_sub:"HolidaiButler combines artificial intelligence with human expertise. Every recommendation, every piece of content and every interaction is powered by AI \u2014 but always controlled and validated by people. No black box, but transparent technology serving the user.",
plat_c1_t:"Hyper-personalised",plat_c1_d:"Real-time recommendations based on profile, preferences, location, weather and time. No generic tips \u2014 always relevant, always personal.",
plat_c2_t:"Local2Local",plat_c2_d:"Local partnerships supporting local economies and identity. Not an anonymous platform, but a bridge between visitors and the community.",
plat_c3_t:"European Compliance as Strength",plat_c3_d:"RaaS \u2014 Regulation as a Service. GDPR, EU AI Act, PCI DSS compliance built into the platform. Trusted and secure from data to payment.",
mod_label:"Modules",mod_title:"Enterprise-grade. Modular. Scalable.",mod_sub:"Each component works independently and is fully integrated. Activate only what you need.",
mod1_t:"POI Management",mod1_d:"Unlimited POIs with 80+ data fields per location, automated quality and freshness control, tier management.",
mod2_t:"Agenda & Events",mod2_d:"Event calendar with automatic categorisation, multilingual display and integration with local and international data sources for the most complete agenda.",
mod3_t:"PubliQio Content Studio",mod3_d:"AI-driven content generation with tone-of-voice per brand, SEO optimisation, multi-platform publishing and performance tracking. Available as a standalone product.",
mod4_t:"HoliBot AI Chatbot",mod4_d:"Multilingual RAG chatbot with POI knowledge, route planning and booking integration. Personal local recommendations 24/7.",
mod5_t:"Website Page Builder",mod5_d:"Configure and publish a complete destination website without code. 35+ blocks, visual editors, live preview, drag-and-drop, tenant theming and server-side rendering for optimal SEO.",
mod6_t:"Commerce & Ticketing",mod6_d:"Ticket sales and reservations with Adyen payments, QR validation, inventory management and automated settlement per partner.",
mod7_t:"Multilingual",mod7_d:"Translate with unmatched accuracy into 100+ languages with one click. DeepL Pro + Mistral AI. Configurable language set per destination.",
mod8_t:"Analytics & Monitoring",mod8_d:"25 AI agents continuously monitor data quality, performance and availability. SimpleAnalytics for privacy-first website tracking.",
mod9_t:"Multi-Tenant Architecture",mod9_d:"One installation, unlimited destinations. Each with its own domain, branding, language set, content and user management. From Texel to Calpe in the same codebase.",
stat1:"API Endpoints",stat2:"Languages",stat3:"Page Builder Blocks",stat4:"AI Agents",stat5:"Platform",
proc_label:"The HolidaiButler Process",proc_title:"From Data, through Experience to Results",
proc_sub:"Automated data pipeline \u2192 modular configuration \u2192 measurable growth. Configure, launch and let AI, guided by our experts, do the work.",
proc_d_label:"Data",proc_d_sub:"Automated \u00b7 Foundation",
proc_d1:"<strong>Hetzner Cloud</strong>EU hosting",proc_d2:"<strong>Periodic data updates</strong>Flexible, accurate, current",proc_d3:"<strong>API integrations</strong>Adyen, Mistral AI, DeepL, MailerLite",
proc_c_label:"Configuration & Modules",proc_c_sub:"Modular \u00b7 White-label \u00b7 No coding",
proc_c1:"<strong>POI Module</strong>Routes, restaurants, attractions, services",proc_c2:"<strong>Agenda Module</strong>Events, multi-source",proc_c3:"<strong>AI Chatbot</strong>Multilingual, 24/7, quick actions, voice",proc_c4:"<strong>Commerce</strong>Tickets, reservations, payments",proc_c5:"<strong>PubliQio</strong>AI Content Studio, media library",
proc_g_label:"Growth",proc_g_sub:"Communication \u00b7 Continuity \u00b7 Time savings",
proc_g1:"<strong>Time</strong>Save 25%+ hours on content and translations",proc_g2:"<strong>Reach</strong>Multilingual visibility, 24/7 availability",proc_g3:"<strong>Impact</strong>AI-driven content, SEO and engagement",
proc_ready:"HolidaiButler is ready. Are you?",
kpi1_t:"\u23f1 Time savings",kpi1_d:"One in three marketers saves 10\u201314 hours per week with AI; another third saves 15+ hours per week.",
kpi2_t:"\u2708\ufe0f Reach",kpi2_d:"40% of active travellers used generative AI for travel planning in 2024 (22% in 2023). Analysts expect 50%+ in 2025.",
kpi3_t:"\ud83d\udcc8 Impact",kpi3_d:"According to European tourism organisations, AI applications for copywriting (68%) and content creation (46%) are the most valuable.",
usp_label:"Why HolidaiButler",usp_title:"No smoke and mirrors. Practical, purposeful, transparent.",
usp1_t:"45 years of expertise",usp1_d:"The founders combine 45 years of strategic, commercial and UI/UX/AI experience. Proven track record in leisure, tourism, marketing and commerce.",
usp2_t:"Regulation as a Service (RaaS)",usp2_d:"European compliance as a competitive advantage. GDPR, EU AI Act, PCI DSS \u2014 not a burden, but a unique selling point towards end-users and partners.",
usp3_t:"Local2Local",usp3_d:"Local partnerships to support local economies and identity. Not an extractive platform \u2014 an ecosystem that gives value back to the destination.",
usp4_t:"Hyper-personalised assistance",usp4_d:"Real-time, accurate information tailored to profile, preferences and context. No generic tips \u2014 always relevant, always personal.",
usp5_t:"Trusted & secure",usp5_d:"From data to payment. End-to-end encryption, EU-hosted infrastructure (Hetzner DE), no data resale, full transparency.",
usp6_t:"Deep sector knowledge",usp6_d:"Data and AI deployed from proven understanding of needs, processes and dynamics in hospitality, leisure and tourism. From both demand and supply side.",
usp7_t:"White label concept",usp7_d:"Applicable to any service organisation in hospitality, leisure and tourism. Own branding, own domain, own identity \u2014 powered by HolidaiButler.",
usp8_t:"Practical & transparent",usp8_d:"No smoke and mirrors. Purposeful technology that delivers immediate value. Transparent AI decisions, measurable results, honest communication.",
sc_label:"Live Projects",sc_title:"Proven in practice.",sc_sub:"No mockups, no demo environments. These are live products helping tourists every day.",
sc1_region:"Costa Blanca, Spain",sc1_stat:"1,600+ POIs \u00b7 4 languages \u00b7 AI Chatbot<br>Commerce \u00b7 Content Studio",sc1_link:"Visit CalpeTrip \u2192",
sc2_region:"Texel, Netherlands",sc2_stat:"1,100+ POIs \u00b7 4 languages \u00b7 AI Chatbot Tessa<br>Event calendar",sc2_link:"Visit TexelMaps \u2192",
sc3_region:"AI Content Studio",sc3_stat:"Standalone product \u00b7 Multi-platform<br>SEO optimisation \u00b7 100+ languages",sc3_link:"Visit PubliQio \u2192",
sc_pipe:"+ WarreWijzer (Limburg, BE) and Alicante (ES) in preparation",
eu_label:"Infrastructure",eu_title:"EU-First Technology Stack",eu_sub:"All data, AI models and infrastructure within the European Union. No exceptions.",
eu_d1:"Content & chatbot AI \u00b7 Paris",eu_d2:"Translations 100+ languages \u00b7 Cologne",eu_d3:"Server & database \u00b7 Gunzenhausen",eu_d4:"Privacy-first analytics \u00b7 Amsterdam",eu_d5:"Payments \u00b7 Amsterdam",eu_d6:"SEO intelligence \u00b7 Bonn",
eu_footer:"No data leaves the European Union. Period.",
